  "notes": "Facing the challenge of increasing client demand and limited clinician resources, Medigold Health wanted to find ways to reduce administrative burdens on clinicians so they can focus more on patient care—and have better work-life balance.\n\nWith Microsoft Azure as a foundation, the Medigold team migrated their applications and use Azure SQL Database for data storage. Azure SQL Database is the main persistence layer for storing AI-generated responses and making them accessible to clinicians through Medigold's internal application.\n \nAutomated processes, especially with report generation, are saving clinicians time, leading to a 58% rise in clinician retention and greater job satisfaction.\n\nhttps://www.microsoft.com/en/customers/story/19709-medigold-health-consultancy-azure"
}